\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces False novelty rate (FNR) by $V$-completeness level (connectivity condition) and classifier accuracy. Error bars show $\pm 1$ std across 30 seeds ($n=200$ hypotheses, 40 latent classes, 20 agents). Across conditions the FNR span is $0.947$; within any condition varying classifier accuracy over 0.60--0.90 moves FNR by $\leq 0.035$. Both ranges are sensitive to their chosen endpoints and are reported descriptively.}}{15}{figure.caption.9}\protected@file@percent }
